SCOAN Sunday Service

0:27:25.940,0:27:32.640
A humble believing soul that truly loves Jesus Christ

0:27:32.640,0:27:37.780
takes everything Jesus says and does it in good faith

0:27:37.780,0:27:45.180
and puts the best construction on it.

0:27:45.180,0:27:48.860
When she heard and she believed, her behaviour changed.

0:27:48.860,0:27:54.880
Immediately, she removed the garment of sorrow and a smile enlightened her face

0:27:54.880,0:28:01.320
because she believed that her request for a child was granted by God

0:28:01.320,0:28:09.620
and indeed, Samuel, the great prophet and judge was born.

