Whatever you are experiencing now that is contrary to your heart's desire - stop!

0:28:33.640,0:28:36.220
Stop thinking about your problem.

0:28:36.220,0:28:40.700
Take time to change your focus because you are in His presence.

0:28:40.700,0:29:02.700
Say, "Neighbour, listen to my voice. If you run out of rope, grab onto faith".

0:29:02.700,0:29:07.340
Don't run from God; run to God

0:29:07.340,0:29:22.380
and that hope, that promise will become a reality.

0:29:22.380,0:29:29.220
Jesus said in John 8:12, "I am the light of the world.

0:29:29.220,0:29:39.500
He who follows Me will never walk in darkness but will have the light of life".

0:29:39.500,0:29:49.360
The only way you can see life clearly is to focus on Jesus.

0:29:49.360,0:29:55.580
It is not your mere wishful thinking but your rightful focus on Him

0:29:55.580,0:30:01.320
that determines who you are before God.

0:30:01.320,0:30:08.940
It is not your mere wishful thinking but your rightful focus

0:30:08.940,0:30:14.100
that determines who you are before God.

0:30:14.100,0:30:21.020
Focus on God, not on the problem.

0:30:21.020,0:30:24.620
Focus on Him.

0:30:24.620,0:30:33.660
What you regard as failure is not failure at all from eternity's perspective.

0:30:33.660,0:30:43.300
That problem, that trouble is not failure from eternity's perspective.

0:30:43.300,0:30:47.680
You need to know what God says about the situation.

0:30:47.680,0:30:50.520
You need to know what God says about you.

0:30:50.520,0:30:53.720
It is within you - it is hidden.

0:30:53.720,0:30:59.180
You need to discover it.

0:30:59.180,0:31:06.940
There is something in you that is dormant - as was my case.

0:31:06.940,0:31:13.600
Today is the day that the Lord has made.

0:31:13.600,0:31:16.900
I will rejoice and be glad in it.

0:31:16.900,0:31:25.860
If you believe, you will rejoice.

0:31:25.860,0:31:34.080
Focus on God Almighty, not on the trouble.

0:31:34.080,0:31:40.280
Your focus determines your response to the situation

0:31:40.280,0:31:46.580
and that response determines your future.

0:31:46.580,0:31:49.000
Look to God.

0:31:49.000,0:31:52.660
Discover it.

0:31:52.660,0:32:00.200
How do you discover it?

0:32:00.200,0:32:12.540
Meditation brings revelation.

0:32:12.540,0:32:19.200
As you are sitting down, that voice of condemnation, that voice of fear,

0:32:19.200,0:32:21.920
what people have been saying about you -

0:32:21.920,0:32:29.480
today, if you believe, you will get out of the wilderness.

0:32:29.480,0:32:36.020
Yielding your heart to the Word of God makes the Word of God a reality.

0:32:36.020,0:32:39.620
Yielding your heart to the Word of God makes the promise a reality

0:32:39.620,0:32:47.320
and when it does - the Bible says, you become Word-minded and God-minded.

0:32:47.320,0:32:55.240
When you are God-minded, you will know the mind of God about you and your situation.

0:32:55.240,0:33:03.400
The illumination of the Spirit of God will settle in your heart the truth from eternity's perspective.

0:33:03.400,0:33:14.720
The illumination of the Spirit of God will settle in my heart today the truth from eternity's perspective.

0:33:14.720,0:33:17.320
Look to Jesus.

0:33:17.320,0:33:25.100
Focusing on Jesus Christ of Nazareth puts everything else in its proper perspective.

0:33:25.100,0:33:31.340
Focusing on Him will put everything else in its proper perspective.

0:33:31.340,0:33:33.220
Are you barren?

0:33:33.220,0:33:38.040
Ask Hannah - you will see fruitfulness instead of barrenness.

0:33:38.040,0:33:42.240
You will see healing instead of sickness.

0:33:42.240,0:33:43.340
Are you poor?

0:33:43.340,0:33:48.580
Ask Jabez - you will see prosperity instead of setback.

0:33:48.580,0:33:50.500
Look to Jesus.

0:33:50.500,0:33:52.380
He has come to change your life.

0:33:52.380,0:34:04.200
He has changed my own; He will change your own if you believe.

0:34:04.200,0:34:11.900
King David, Daniel, Simon Peter, along with many heroes of faith -

0:34:11.900,0:34:18.620
they all struggled with various doubts in their lives

0:34:18.620,0:34:26.140
but they focused steadfastly on God Almighty and they prayed without ceasing.

0:34:26.140,0:34:30.020
