0:34:30.020,0:34:36.500
they lost no time in committing their lives to God Almighty.

0:34:36.500,0:34:51.380
The secret of a successful life is to learn to focus on God, not on the happenings around you.

0:34:51.380,0:34:53.680
Focus on Him.

0:34:53.680,0:35:04.040
No matter how unsteady your life appears to be, focus on God.

0:35:04.040,0:35:06.360
Engage your heart.

0:35:06.360,0:35:17.420
As you are sitting down, meditate on the Word of God and whatever you do will prosper.

0:35:17.420,0:35:19.560
Keep focus.

0:35:19.560,0:35:26.900
Tell your neighbour, "Keep focus; identify your Source".

0:35:26.900,0:35:29.220
Who is your Source?

0:35:29.220,0:35:34.780
Jesus Christ of Nazareth who raised the dead will change your life.

0:35:34.780,0:35:38.620
When you look at Him, you will see your life clearly.

